Oxfam Website Content Summary

Period between 2018-11-27 and 2018-12-11.

•Data filtered for content > 50 page views during the specified time period.
•Average engaged time: The amount of actively engaged time (in seconds) per page view.
•Quality Depth: Ratio of page views that scrolled to at least 50% of the page.
•Continued Journey: Ratio of page views that went to another page on our website.
•Percent Organic Traffic: organic traffic is traffic that comes to our content through organic search, direct, or referall links from other sources. All other methods are considered to be promoted by Oxfam in some way. A lower percentage on this metric indicates a higher level of promotion.
•Green bolded values indicate content that was in the top 75th percentile for the given metric relative to all other content in the dataset.
•Red bolded values indicate content that was in the lower 25th percentile for the given metric relative to all other content in the dataset.
